Longer-term but genuinely viable. Hayeong running YouTube channels with AI-generated content. The value extends beyond ad revenue: brand for Etsy store, showcase of capabilities, affiliate income platform.

| **ASMR / Ambient Video** | Best starting point. Lowest production complexity. ComfyUI feeds imagery. Audio via TTS + soundscapes. Looping ambient content performs well. James watches ASMR regularly — natural niche fit. |
