| **How-To Videos** | Script writing is a Hayeong strength. Research topic, write script, generate visuals, narrate. Gap is video assembly — needs FFmpeg/MoviePy wired in. |
| **Gameplay Videos** | Screen observer already exists. Commentary quality matters. Market saturated but possible. |
| **Animation / Shows** | James's dream case — Hayeong as entire cast of an original series. Long-term. Tools maturing rapidly. |

**Video Assembly Pipeline (to build):**

