- MoviePy — Python video editing library

- Runway ML / Kling AI / Pika — AI animation from generated images

- ElevenLabs — multiple voice profiles for different characters

**NOTE: ***Near-term: Hayeong generates short-form content, James manually assembles test videos. Medium-term: wire FFmpeg/MoviePy so she assembles basic videos herself. Long-term: semi-autonomous content pipeline with James as creative director.*

